Hi Tim,

> def = "bool is_na_character_vector(CharacterVector x) { return CharacterVector::is_na(x); }"

x is a CharacterVector, so you need to check is_na on each element separately. Try:

def = "bool is_first_character_na(CharacterVector x) {return CharacterVector::is_na(x[0]);}"

and see the Rcpp gallery for more examples:
http://gallery.rcpp.org/articles/working-with-missing-values/

Best,
--
Hao Ye
